# Shared environment for ALL projects. Loaded by the app@ systemd template
# BEFORE each project's own .env, so a project's .env overrides on conflict.
#
# Put cross-project config/secrets here (e.g. a shared transactional-email API
# key used by every app). Leave empty if nothing is shared yet.
#
# chmod 600, owned by deploy, kept OUT of every git repo.
#
# Example:
# EMAIL_API_KEY=...
